::DarkMouse::

She looked at the pool of mech fluid on the floor around her feet.
It had gotten deeper, much deeper.
She sighed, "I wonder, was it worth it." She slumped down to the 
floor. She looked out but didn't see anything.  "Hey, commander. I'm 
sorry if I got you into trouble. I mean, I never meant too....."
she voice drifted off. The light flickered and faded from her eyes.

She spark joined the Matrix.


Please put DarkMouse on the Deceased list. Killed by Stegotron and 
the other Dinobots.
